{"tid":2298564,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中西區觀龍】梁晃維區務親力親為 挽泛民形象","createTime":"2020-11-24T06:49:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T07:17:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9c973d0c0931582550737c64e69d7bbe89f4306e","tid":2298564,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T06:49:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201124/SO76NYAYSNAZDCITKZTMG37JT4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201124%2FSO76NYAYSNAZDCITKZTMG37JT4%2F&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaN%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=31498d6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201124%2FSO76NYAYSNAZDCITKZTMG37JT4%2F&h=1f27ca40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201124/SO76NYAYSNAZDCITKZTMG37JT4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【中西區觀龍】梁晃維區務親力親為 挽泛民形象<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UckG4a8LHaghjRQieCU3zTVRszU=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YBTR3HXW6RDLVNA7OAP6HTC62A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUckG4a8LHaghjRQieCU3zTVRszU%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYBTR3HXW6RDLVNA7OAP6HTC62A.jpg&h=7e78d5c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■梁晃維表示，區議員透過地區工作建立的網絡，在任期後仍很有價值。<br />\n<br />\n梁晃維位於觀龍樓的議辦地方狹窄，訪問於是移師到室外進行。但由議辦走到樓下的休憩空間卻困難重重，他沿路接了三通居民的求助電話。原來除了開會時間，議辦所有來電他都親自接聽，不假手於助理。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【屯門新墟】張可森牽頭趕走大媽 還公園寧靜<br />\n<br />\n「我想俾人睇到我同以前嘅人有唔同。」梁晃維接觸街坊後發現，即使他們認同建制派在社區的實力，很少人形容前議員是「親力親為」，多數靠助理處理街坊求助，「最後議員淨係簽個名。呢個係我想改變嘅風氣」。梁晃維指出，區內很多獨居長者，他們最缺乏的就是陪伴，因此經常現身很重要，社區工作要盡量親自出動，「要維繫社區網絡，好靠自己本身嘅親和力，或者願意投入幾多。」<br />\n<br />\n在觀龍區當選的梁晃維如此着緊不無道理。。。。。。。。。。一例子，以後一定要杜絕。<br />\n<br />\n去年的情況正正與03年選舉雷同。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n雖然反抗浪潮席捲全港，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不想選民感遺棄<br />\n<br />\n因此，梁晃維上任初時時常提醒自己，必須勤於區務，否則選民再次失望，就不會再給予第二次機會，民主派可永別觀龍選區。他的表現是否有較何秀蘭好？90歲的何伯住在區內超過60年，是永恒的建制支持者。他對何秀蘭已無印象，而「青年人」雖然不及建制好，但至少「民建聯有做嘅佢都有做」，有居民會議、有聚餐必定會通知他，最少合格。<br />\n<br />\n在這背景下，梁晃維當初決定參選立法會，都經過一番掙扎。當時有傳媒率先傳出他有意參選，有居民就來質問他：「係咪真係諗清楚呀？」他因此有猶豫：「會唔會重複當年嘅錯誤？」到後來收集提名時，他卻發現本區居民的反應非常正面，不少人主動簽名，他才放下心頭大石，原來觀龍居民已不再只要一個「街坊保長」。<br />\n<br />\n但最終白掙扎一場，高唱「熱愛基本法」的梁晃維照被選舉主任查問，政權甚至連整個選舉都取消。自此，他對區務的想法起了轉變，既然自己甚至同路人都未必可以再參選，工作目標就不再與選舉、選票相關，而是要盡量做好自己，讓居民看到民主陣營和親北京陣營的分別。到他無法參選之時，居民自然看穿制度荒謬。<br />\n<br />\n除了凡事親力親為，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他還把建制派不會觸碰的議題帶入社區，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n但香港不斷加速敗壞，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n「區議會最重要嘅資源就係個社區網絡，。。。。。。。。。。價值。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iMezllTLaD8UJBt24hmdZdAx4y8=/1135x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FAIYJDWVYVFYXIPSNJPPFBS7EI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiMezllTLaD8UJBt24hmdZdAx4y8%3D%2F1135x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFAIYJDWVYVFYXIPSNJPPFBS7EI.jpg&h=61f8be68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■何秀蘭（左）2003年在觀龍選區擊敗葉國謙 ，成為一時佳話。"},{"pid":"7923239b0eb511bd6ae0566f7fa0f1bb33bd4303","tid":2298564,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T06:55:49.000Z","msg":"佢唔係本土派咩"},{"pid":"8333d49d3b273f74f19da3d189fca644576429a3","tid":2298564,"uid":283071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T06:57:44.000Z","msg":"我係咪要調整標準 <br />\n總之唔係建制就係泛民？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b53463ab86dc129231e194e14310ed51e53cae","tid":2298564,"uid":50196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T06:57:59.000Z","msg":"梁晃維被泛民<br />\n蘋果好撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4acbb5d3e798ae53cea40f913b602ac51930ecd","tid":2298564,"uid":279492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T07:04:42.000Z","msg":"佢好過葉國謙<br />\n利申 觀龍區住了30年"},{"pid":"c98f5cc141b368acb76c89be8fc8c543626dc628","tid":2298564,"uid":10241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T07:06:14.000Z","msg":"總之唔係建制就係泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沒第3樣揀"},{"pid":"5463ecda24e20a34e633a493350f8e3ded3ffe90","tid":2298564,"uid":34970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T07:07:10.000Z","msg":"騎劫？"},{"pid":"91da16f543efdf3c9ef5664d4db64512af121f11","tid":2298564,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7923239b0eb511bd6ae0566f7fa0f1bb33bd4303","tid":2298564,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T06:55:49.000Z","msg":"佢唔係本土派咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T07:07:30.000Z","msg":"毒果"},{"pid":"1dbee277d120b2ad71cce1dcace540a8d9d70b5c","tid":2298564,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7923239b0eb511bd6ae0566f7fa0f1bb33bd4303","tid":2298564,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T06:55:49.000Z","msg":"佢唔係本土派咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T07:11:17.000Z","msg":"梁晃維 上D100邊有可系 本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/qqEzDhPxYCk/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FqqEzDhPxYCk%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=7f18308a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9a76cfdbae793866b13e9ef3ad767ed0cc0b76e","tid":2298564,"uid":1435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T07:17:24.000Z","msg":"屌講起何秀蘭就興<br />\n佢根本個心就想入立會，贏完一屆就即刻大敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}